branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The CE1 series is a stroke reading cylinder with position feedback. The home position can be anywhere within the cylinder stroke. Measurement is possible throughout the full stroke range. The CE1 series is offered in 6 bore sizes and is auto switch capable.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchCategory.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stroke reading cylinder with position feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Resolution: 0.1mm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Water resistance improved by changing sensor unit filter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Power supply voltage 12 to 24V DC&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Numerous stroke variations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improved noise resistance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bore sizes: 12, 20, 32, 40, 50, 63&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

